<title>bḥb yswʿ lạ̉nh byḥmyny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥb yswʿ lạ̉nh byḥmyny wyqwyny dạymạaⁿ ʿly̱ ạlsẖyṭạn
 wmhmạ jh ạblys yzʿlny wykẖlyny mạsbḥsẖ ạlrb yswʿ
 ạlqrạr - hạqwlh lạ̉ hạqwlh lạ̉ hạqwlh lạ̉ rwḥ ạmsẖy bʿyd
 (ạ̉nạ bḥb ạlrb yswʿ whạfḍl ạ̉sbḥ lyh)2
 2- bḥb yswʿ lạ̉nh bynṣrny ʿly̱ ạlsẖyṭạn lmạ yḥạrbny
 wyḥạwl ymnʿny ạ̉sẖkr yswʿ wyqwly ạtnrfz wạḍrb wạsẖtm wạkdb wạḥlf</lyrics>
</song>